## Issues Identified

1. **CRITICAL**: Components section overwrites schemas
   - Impact: No schemas documented in OpenAPI spec
   - Impact: ErrorResponse and all other model schemas missing
   - Location: apps/server/src/docs/mod.rs:20-32 (AuthSecurityAddon.modify)
   - Fix needed: Modify existing components instead of replacing

2. **MODERATE**: Placeholder endpoints not in OpenAPI spec
   - Impact: Future development endpoints not documented
